June 1, 1970* No. 1409,

Misc.

Harris v. City of Houston et al.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of the orders of this date.

Appeal from Dist. Ct. of Harris County, Tex., dismissed for want of jurisdiction. Treating the papers whereon the appeal was taken as a petition for a writ of certiorari, certiorari denied.
